      <title>法国财政部长承诺预算将遵守欧盟规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/french-finance-minister-promises-budget-will-respect-eu-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长安托万·阿尔芒表示，政府将在本周提交一份遵守欧盟规则的预算，以安抚欧盟合作伙伴和市场对法国失控赤字的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/french-finance-minister-promises-budget-will-respect-eu-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 08:25:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯袭击以色列，引发更大范围冲突。一年后，以色列再次爆发冲突。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/hamas-struck-israel-for-a-wider-conflict-a-year-later-it-s-got-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 月 7 日的袭击是几十年来最严重的政治暴力行为之一。它的影响仍然在全球产生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/hamas-struck-israel-for-a-wider-conflict-a-year-later-it-s-got-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦下令调查两名中国人在武装袭击中丧生事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/pakistan-orders-inquiry-as-two-chinese-killed-in-militant-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦正在调查周日在港口城市卡拉奇发生的导致两名中国公民死亡的袭击事件，目前这个南亚国家正努力遏制针对其主要经济伙伴利益的日益高涨的激进活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/pakistan-orders-inquiry-as-two-chinese-killed-in-militant-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击加沙以阻止哈马斯再次发动袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-strikes-across-gaza-to-thwart-renewed-hamas-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列星期一轰炸了加沙全境的哈马斯目标，以阻止所谓的“即时”火箭弹威胁，该组织计划在一年前发动毁灭性袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-strikes-across-gaza-to-thwart-renewed-hamas-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政府寻求提高通胀目标以降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/thai-government-seeks-higher-inflation-target-to-enable-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，泰国财政部计划将明年通胀目标提高至1.5%-3.5%，这给央行下调基准利率带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/thai-government-seeks-higher-inflation-target-to-enable-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡前部长被判入狱，不会就里程碑案件上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/singapore-ex-minister-says-will-not-appeal-court-sentence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[易华仁 (S. Iswaran) 向新加坡法庭自首，成为近半个世纪以来第一位被判入狱的前内阁部长，这一丑闻让这座以善治为荣的城市关注不已。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/singapore-ex-minister-says-will-not-appeal-court-sentence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:28:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>支持对华电动汽车关税的欧盟国家面临最大报复风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-s-yes-votes-on-china-ev-tariffs-seen-as-targets-for-revenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税，人们的焦点转向北京将如何以及何时对欧盟多年来最大的贸易争端升级采取报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-s-yes-votes-on-china-ev-tariffs-seen-as-targets-for-revenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本财长加藤警告日元突然波动可能带来负面影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/japan-s-kato-says-sudden-fx-moves-have-negative-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新任财务大臣表示，在日元最近几天大幅下跌之后，日元汇率的突然波动对企业和家庭造成了损害，这种影响需要政府进行密切关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/japan-s-kato-says-sudden-fx-moves-have-negative-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不到 100 天，Starmer 就被迫陷入混乱的重置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/starmer-forced-into-messy-reset-less-than-100-days-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 更换了他的高级助手，财政部承认关键的增税计划正在审查中，工党政府试图纠正连盟友都说执政三个月以来的艰难历程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/starmer-forced-into-messy-reset-less-than-100-days-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 23:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级铀矿开采商投票决定恢复核电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/world-s-top-uranium-miner-holds-nuclear-power-plant-referendum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦选民将于周日决定是否允许建造核电站，因为人们担心核电站对环境的影响，以及可能依赖这个中亚国家的两个巨型邻国——中国和俄罗斯——的技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/world-s-top-uranium-miner-holds-nuclear-power-plant-referendum</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
